00:27:12,233 --> 00:27:13,720
Guest: Yeah, I did.

414
00:27:13,841 --> 00:27:15,770
Guest: I did my undergrad in philosophy and in physics.

415
00:27:16,291 --> 00:27:20,650
Guest: So it's a bachelor's degree, which, oh, but, you know, that's all I got.

416
00:27:20,911 --> 00:27:21,305
Guest: One of those.

