722
00:45:06,829 --> 00:45:08,294
Guest: You can go and work on Wall Street.

723
00:45:08,616 --> 00:45:09,740
Guest: You can go and work for Google.

724
00:45:10,200 --> 00:45:13,994
Guest: You can go do a lot of different things with a physics major.

725
00:45:14,014 --> 00:45:15,660
Guest: I mean, you can go into patent law.

726
00:45:16,020 --> 00:45:16,779
Scott: Unlike a philosophy major?

727
00:45:18,521 --> 00:45:18,721
Guest: Yeah.

728
00:45:18,962 --> 00:45:31,140
